        <num>CCP 3283</num>
        <heading>3283.  Who may file opposition</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3283.  Who may file opposition
An opposition to a proposed private sale of succession property may be filed only by an heir, legatee, or creditor.</p>
        </content>
